name: The Showcase: #21 If you can Dream It You Can Do It! Shirt
description:
The twenty-first Tshirt in our showcase. A collection of 200 different 1/1 Tshirts in total made by DoYouCrypto. Be ready to experience the old and new crypto history. #20 If you can Dream It You Can Do It! This design was made during the first big  Bitcoin rallye in 2017. 

As part of objkt4objkt this piece will be 10000 edition! All unsold will be burned after 48h!
